---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BookingButton from '../components/BookingButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Workshops for Organizations | promptwork.shop"
  description="Transform your organization with expert-led AI workshops. Learn to leverage AI effectively through hands-on training tailored to your industry."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    headline="If AI Feels Important But Unclear, You're Not Alone"
    subheadline="Most people are somewhere between curiosity and confusion. Let's fix that."
  />

  <!-- Normalize Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">
          You're Not Behind, You're <span class="text-brand-primary-600">Normal</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Somewhere between the hype, the panic, and the third "AI strategy" meeting that produced no strategy, most people landed in the same place: confused but nodding along.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
          The ones who figure it out aren't smarter. They just started.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Real Problem Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-h2 font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 text-center">
          The Problem Isn't Lack of Information
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          There's too much information. What you actually need is direction and hands-on practice.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Everyone Has Different Advice</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              The vendors want to sell you platforms. The consultants want to sell you strategies. Meanwhile, you're trying to figure out what to actually do.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">The Jargon Is Overwhelming</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              "LLM," "agents," "hallucinations;" you've heard the buzzwords. But turning them into something you can actually use? That's the hard part.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Generic Playbooks Don't Work</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              Every industry has different constraints and needs. You don't need a one-size-fits-all solution. You need something that works in your world.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Demos Don't Translate to Reality</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              You've seen the cool prototypes. But turning a demo into something useful day-to-day? That's where most "AI initiatives" quietly disappear.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Changes Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-h2 font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 text-center">
          What Changes After a Workshop
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A workshop won't solve every AI challenge. But it will give you direction — and the confidence to actually start.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-800 text-lg">You move from "we should probably do something with AI" to "we actually know where to start"</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-800 text-lg">You stop feeling intimidated and start feeling capable</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-800 text-lg">You learn through hands-on practice, not theory or slide decks</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-800 text-lg">You get a practical framework you can actually remember and use on Monday morning</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries Served Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-h2 font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 text-center">
          Who This Is For
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-12 text-center">
          If AI feels important but unclear, you're in the right place.
        </p>

        <!-- Industry Cards -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <!-- Education -->
          <a href="/education" class="block transition-transform hover:scale-105">
            <div class="bg-brand-primary-50 border-2 border-brand-primary-500 rounded-xl p-8 h-full">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
                Educators & Schools
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-700">
                Teachers, administrators, and districts trying to make sense of AI without adding another thing to the pile.
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Teams -->
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 border-2 border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-8 opacity-75">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
              Teams Who Need Practical Wins
            </h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              Organizations that don't need another keynote. You need to know how AI fits into your work this week, not next quarter.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Leaders -->
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 border-2 border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-8 opacity-75">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
              Leaders Figuring It Out
            </h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              You've been asked to "have an AI strategy." You're smart enough to know you don't have one yet. That's the starting line.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA Section -->
  <section class="relative section-padding overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-accent-500 via-brand-accent-600 to-brand-primary-600">
    <!-- Decorative background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_30%,rgba(255,255,255,0.1),transparent_50%)]"></div>

    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Ready to Start?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 text-white/95 leading-relaxed">
          Book a conversation. We'll talk about your situation — your challenges, your constraints, your goals — and figure out what a workshop would look like for you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 text-white/95 leading-relaxed">
          No pressure. No sales pitch. Just an honest discussion about whether we can help.
        </p>
        <BookingButton
          variant="secondary"
          size="lg"
          href="mailto:book@promptwork.shop?subject=Workshop%20Inquiry"
          text="Book A Workshop"
          class="bg-white text-brand-primary-600 hover:bg-neutral-50 border-0 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
